All Implemented Interfaces:
com.trolltech.qt.QtJambiInterface
public class Downloader
extends com.trolltech.qt.core.QObject

Downloads timetable in form of xml. Asks for login with login dialog and download timetable xml from IS. IS timetable url is stored in file conf/timetableUrl. When the loading is done it emits a signal for parser.

Version:
2012-06-04
Author:
Michal Kimle
